<text xml:lang="ta">
  <body>
    <div xml:id="PN221-intro">
      <p type="edition">tiṇaiyum tuṟaiyum avai. avaṉ naṭukaṟkaṇṭu avar pāṭiyatu.
      </p>
      <p xml:lang="en" type="translation">  
      </p>
    </div>
    <div xml:id="PN221">
      <lg type="edition">
<l>pāṭunark kītta palpuka ḻaṉṉē</l>
<l>yāṭunark kītta pēraṉ piṉaṉē</l>
<l>yaṟavōr pukaḻnta vāykō laṉṉē</l>
<l>tiṟavōr pukaḻnta tiṇṇaṇ piṉaṉē</l>
<l>makaḷir cāyaṉ maintarkku maintu</l>
<l>tukaḷaṟu kēḷvi yuyarntōr pukki</l>
<l>laṉaiya ṉeṉṉā tattak kōṉai</l>
<l>niṉaiyāk kūṟṟa miṉṉuyi ruyttaṉṟu</l>
<l>paita lokkaṟ ṟaḻīi yataṉai</l>
<l>vaikam vammō vāymoḻip pulavīr</l>
<l>naṉantalai yulaka marantai tūṅkka</l>
<l>keṭuvi ṉallicai cūṭi</l>
<l>naṭuka lāyiṉaṉ puravala ṉeṉavē.</l>
</lg>
<lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l corresp="1">  He is one much praised who gives to singers. </l>
<l corresp="2">  He has great love who gives to dancers. </l>
<l corresp="3">  He has a discerning sceptre praise by the virtuous. </l>
<l corresp="4">  He has firm friendship praised by the informed. </l>
<l corresp="5">  Graceful to women, to the mighty ones might, </l>
<l corresp="6">  a refuge to those high in flawless erudition </l>
<l>  – not saying he is such a one, not thinking him</l>
<l>  that paragon Death has dispatched [his] sweet life. (7f.)</l>
<l>  Embracing [our] suffering kinfolk, come,</l>
<l>  we we curse him, o scholars of true words, (9f.)</l>
<l corresp="13d">    thinking that, </l>
<l corresp="11">  while the world of vast area is suspended in affliction, </l>
<l corresp="12">  wearing fame that does not get lost </l>
<l corresp="13">  [our] protector has become a hero stone. </l>
</lg>
    </div>
